    - target: {fileID: 7167559663983844740, guid: 265795e21582a0647bc33ee5c1480dfb, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '<b>Credits

        </b>





        A game by wolfheat













        A
        variety of assets were used to create this game.





        <b>Graphic</b>

        3D

        Synty
        Studio Asset Packs

        Ancient Empire

        Construction

        Kids

        Mini
        City

        NightClub

        Office

        Town



        Gece Studio
        - Dragon Head



        2D

        Vector Dividers Collection -  Start
        menu Dividers

        Kenney - Icons from asset packs

        Zooperdan
        - Printer Display Image

        avatar

        macrovector - Postit

        Ben
        Clark - Vector Notes



        VFX

        Unity Technologies - Particle
        Pack



        <b>Audio</b>



        FreeSounds,Pixabay - Various Sounds
        assets

        Uppbeat - Music



        <b>Music</b>

        Brock Hewitt
        - In The Silence

        Monument Music - Love Story



        <b>Fonts</b>

        Prida01
        - gluk



        <b>Tools Used</b>

        Audacity

        Gimp

        Blender

        Unity



        <b>Game
        Jam</b>

        This game was created for the

        Dungeon Crawler Game
        Jam 2026



'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
