    - target: {fileID: 7258905331927034073, guid: c5146402ccb695c43b28291e80f6e2db, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '<b>Credits

        </b>



        A game by wolfheat







        A
        variety of assets were used to create this game.



        <b>Graphics

        </b>

        3D

        Pure
        Poly - Ultimate Low Poly Mining

        BitGem - Hand Painted Series

        Siuniaev
        - Gambler Cat

        Instant Zoomies - Horror Starter Pack Free

        Synty
        - Ancient Empire



        2D

        Vector Dividers Collection

        upklyak
        (freepik) - Ground cracks on land isolated



        VFX

        Unity
        Technologies - Particle Pack



        <b>Audio

        </b>

        Freesound
        - Various Sounds

        Pixabay - Various Sounds

        Uppbeat - Music



        <b>Music

        </b>

        Brock
        Hewitt - In The Silence

        Monument Music - Love Story



        <b>Fonts

        </b>

        Prida01
        - gluk



        <b>AI Tools

        </b>

        Playground AI - 2D art

        Craiyon
        - 2D art

        Piclumen - 2D art

        Suno - Music



        <b>Other
        Tools Used

        </b>

        Audacity

        Gimp

        Blender

        Unity



        <b>Game
        Jam

        </b>

        This game was created for the

        Dungeon
        Crawler Game Jam 2025





'
